title: [Medicine] The interim Phase III results of the Oxford/AstraZeneca COVID-19 vaccine (ChAdOx1 nCoV-19), have been published in The Lancet. Overall efficacy was 70.4% and found to be efficacious against symptomatic COVID-19 with an acceptable safety profile.
[Medicine] Detection of SARS-CoV-2 antibodies is insufficient for the diagnosis of active or cured COVID-19
